{"tid":2327880,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"中國人喊抵制《RM》！網揪真相酸：身體很誠實","createTime":"2020-12-16T10:05:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T10:41:48.000Z","uid":16659,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"99c480066b529d89d28bc0835b00f26550bb722e","tid":2327880,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T10:05:23.000Z","msg":"南韓人氣節目「Running man」2010年開播至今深受民眾喜愛，不過日前製作單位準備的大富翁地圖上，遭中國網友揪出有台灣國旗，引發中國網友群起撻伐，揚言要抵制。事隔多日，中國影片網站嗶哩嗶哩（簡稱B站）仍照常上架最新一期的「Running Man」，台灣網友見狀大酸「嘴巴說不要，身體到是挺誠實的嘛！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/08/2924549-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F08%2F2924549-PH.jpg&h=40b18bec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲南韓人氣節目「Running Man」2010年開播至今深受民眾喜愛。（圖／翻攝自（圖／翻攝自Running Man IG）<br />\n<br />\nRunning Man於本月7日播出的節目中，遭中國網友揪出節目遊戲使用的大富翁地圖，出現「中國北京」、「台灣台北」字樣，且上面分別印上中國五星旗及我國國旗，引發中國網友爆怒，紛紛要求節目出面道歉，更揚言要抵制該節目。隨後，《微博》立刻大動作清除有關Running Man字眼的文章，至今微博上打出「Running Man」仍無搜尋結果。事隔一週，常針對時事評論，吸引大批網友追蹤的「DJ金寶」今（16）日在臉書上貼出一張B站擷圖，只見圖中Running Man影片皆為最新一期，且網站上仍可見大量的Running Man影片，讓他忍不住開酸「上星期辱華、被中國網民發起罷看的Running Man，本星期時間一到、通通在網站上架啦～」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/16/2938484-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F16%2F2938484-PH.jpg&h=31ad35fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲網友發現中國影片平台仍照常上傳Running Man影片。（圖／「DJ金寶」臉書）<br />\n<br />\n底下網友也紛紛在底下留言大酸「抗韓是工作&hellip;&hellip;看韓綜是生活仇日是工作&hellip;&hellip;買日產保養品是生活，中國人就是傲__嬌」、「嘴巴說不要，身體到是挺誠實的嘛，真是口嫌体正直的最好表現」、「中國人的日常，全世界都知道」、「他們轉換人格也蠻辛苦啦」、「罷看是工作，週更是生活」、「辱華賞味期一週限定」、「NBA也是」。"},{"pid":"b4b743abd1fdf8d4c1f7e191126cc2526f7a39d8","tid":2327880,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T10:06:55.000Z","msg":"咩名黎架....<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f461cb88edab357e85966f9a04315c0339ba07e","tid":2327880,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4b743abd1fdf8d4c1f7e191126cc2526f7a39d8","tid":2327880,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T10:06:55.000Z","msg":"咩名黎架....<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T10:08:32.000Z","msg":"好名好名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de0a7528287cb6aa271c431212336513d7ec5b07","tid":2327880,"uid":61207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T10:10:14.000Z","msg":"愛國只是工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51151da27a6b5f0f0ea5a2ec973f811b01c273f2","tid":2327880,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T10:22:15.000Z","msg":"俾啲骨氣出嚟好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ddeebf49f54b3a843ab2c4da1417871143d9454","tid":2327880,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51151da27a6b5f0f0ea5a2ec973f811b01c273f2","tid":2327880,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T10:22:15.000Z","msg":"俾啲骨氣出嚟好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T10:27:54.000Z","msg":"抵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5636cea8cd4c934514a1c170cb0fb6ef2756d574","tid":2327880,"uid":296191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T10:37:09.000Z","msg":"變咗藍字 爭啲唔認得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a252acd3e5ed177c5908cddd525ba01f93e403ad","tid":